      <body>Confirm this but not only for globbing.

For example this route:

    match &quot;/:path&quot; =&gt; &quot;pages#show&quot;, :constraints =&gt; {:path =&gt; /.+(\/.+)*/ }

    assert_routing '/directory/filename', :controller =&gt; 'pages', :action =&gt; 'show', :path =&gt; 'directory/filename'

    The generated path &lt;&quot;/directory%2Ffilename&quot;&gt; did not match &lt;&quot;/directory/filename&quot;&gt;

Patch solves the problem.</body>
      <body-html>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Confirm this but not only for globbing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For example this route:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;
&lt;code&gt;match &quot;/:path&quot; =&amp;gt; &quot;pages#show&quot;, :constraints =&amp;gt; {:path =&amp;gt; /.+(\/.+)*/ }

assert_routing '/directory/filename', :controller =&amp;gt; 'pages', :action =&amp;gt; 'show', :path =&amp;gt; 'directory/filename'

The generated path &amp;lt;&quot;/directory%2Ffilename&quot;&amp;gt; did not match &amp;lt;&quot;/directory/filename&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Patch solves the problem.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
